		<div>Are you truly bad? Is he truly better? How do you 2 compare in an actual combat situation?<br />
<br />
 <br />
I ask because in EQ1, stats meant different things depending on class, so a 50 Wizard and a 50 Warrior with the same AC and attack rating would fare worlds apart in hand to hand combat.</div>
