		<div>Thats a good point. I havent actually parsed our effectiveness etc. Even in EQ1 though, My wizard had a much lower attack score than an ogre warrior due to his higher strength, dexterity, weapon skill etc etc. This was in addition to the fact that even with the same attack scores I would have been less effective due to being a wizard.<br />
<br />
I mean its not that big of a deal to me. I can hold agro without much trouble even with my low damage output... damaging the mobs is not my job (especially since Im going to go guardian) but I would like to understand things.</div>
